-- SocGen Plans to Open 480 Branches in Africa in Next Five Years, Echos Says
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-11-15T05:31:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-15/socgen-plans-to-open-480-branches-in-africa-in-next-five-years-echos-says.html
Societe Generale plans to open 480
branches in Africa over the next five years in a bid to capture
1.7 million retail clients, French daily Les Echos reported,
without saying where it got the information.  Eighty percent of the new branches are planned in Morocco,
Tunisia, Algeria and Egypt, according to Les Echos.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  